{{Infobox Figure Skating Competition | title= 1974 Prague Skate | image= | imagesize= | caption= | comptype= | startdate= November 08 | enddate= 10 | skatingseason= 1974–75 | location= [[Prague]] | host= | venue= | prizemoney= | championmen= {{flagathlete|[[Terry Kubicka]]|USA}} | championladies= {{flagathlete|[[Kath Malmberg]]|USA}} | championpairs= | championdance= | previouscomp= [[1973 Prague Skate]] | nextcomp= [[1975 Prague Skate]] | previousgp= | nextgp= }}
The International Figure Skating Competition was held in November 8–10, 1974. Medals were awarded in the disciplines of [[single skating|men's singles and ladies' singles]].
